videos.headline: Georgia's LeCounte catches deflected pass for INT
videos.description: Baylor QB Charlie Brewer's pass bounces off Trevor Ebner's hands and into Georgia DB Richard LeCounte's hands for the interception.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Georgia's LeCounte catches deflected pass for INT) 2020/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Fromm finds Pickens on flea-flicker
videos.description: Georgia QB Jake Fromm calls for a flea-flicker and then finds WR George Pickens down the field for a gain of 46 yards.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Fromm finds Pickens on flea-flicker) 2020/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Fromm drops in perfect TD pass to Pickens
videos.description: Georgia QB Jake Fromm delivers a pass right where it needs to be as WR George Pickens makes the grab for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Fromm drops in perfect TD pass to Pickens) 2020/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Fromm connects with Landers for TD
videos.description: Georgia QB Jake Fromm tosses it 16 yards into the end zone where WR Matt Landers secures it for the score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Fromm connects with Landers for TD) 2020/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Baylor's Mims makes leaping TD grab
videos.description: Baylor QB Charlie Brewer sends the ball over to WR Denzel Mims, who makes a leaping catch for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Baylor's Mims makes leaping TD grab) 2020/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Georgia's defensive coordinator fired up after sack-fumble
videos.description: Georgia LB Azeez Ojulari forces a sack-fumble on Baylor QB Charlie Brewer and defensive coordinator Dan Lanning is excited about it.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Georgia's defensive coordinator fired up after sack-fumble) 2020/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Georgia pulls off fake field goal for a first down
videos.description: Georgia sets up for a field goal, but Jake Camarda takes the snap, immediately runs with it and gets enough for a first down.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Georgia pulls off fake field goal for a first down) 2020/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: White turns the corner and scores the TD
videos.description: Zamir White takes the pitch and goes 13 yards for the Georgia touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (White turns the corner and scores the TD) 2020/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Baylor's Brewer pushes forward for the TD
videos.description: Baylor QB Charlie Brewer calls his own number, bounces off a tackle and gets across the goal line for the score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Baylor's Brewer pushes forward for the TD) 2020/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Baylor's Brewer hurt after late hit
videos.description: Baylor QB Charlie Brewer attempts to scramble for a first down and is hit late along the sideline. Brewer eventually leaves the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Baylor's Brewer hurt after late hit) 2020/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Georgia's LeCounte gets spiked shoulder pads after INT
videos.description: Georgia DB Richard LeCounte picks off Baylor QB Jacob Zeno late in the fourth and then LeCounte is gifted spiked shoulder pads on the sidelines.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Georgia's LeCounte gets spiked shoulder pads after INT) 2020/01/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Fromm: Georgia played their hearts out
videos.description: Georgia QB Jake Fromm is proud of they way his team played in their 26-14 win over Baylor in the Allstate Sugar Bowl.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Fromm: Georgia played their hearts out) 2020/01/02

videos.headline: Smart credits seniors for Sugar Bowl win
videos.description: Georgia head coach Kirby Smart praises his seniors for their efforts to lead the team in a 26-14 win vs. Baylor in the Sugar Bowl.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Smart credits seniors for Sugar Bowl win) 2020/01/01 ESHEET
